    "body": "@rkrasiuk \r\n\r\n# Preliminary Investigation \r\n\r\n- In order to determine which files contain the logic,  So far I was able to determine that the `cast wallet commands` are [`HERE`](https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/master/cli/src/cmd/cast/wallet/mod.rs#L20)  defined in the enum `pub enum WalletSubcommands` ,  and its `implementation` is [`HERE`](https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/master/cli/src/cmd/cast/wallet/mod.rs#L77) \r\n- There is no real logic being tested , I am just determining where I need to actually add the logic later\r\n\r\n## Testing Injected Code\r\n\r\n_So for testing I added new field in `pub enum WalletSubcommands`_\r\n- Inserted at [`https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/master/cli/src/cmd/cast/wallet/mod.rs#L20`](https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/master/cli/src/cmd/cast/wallet/mod.rs#L20)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82266083/216162476-4bae5aa8-7190-4c07-876c-83a312249021.png)\r\n\r\n_And a test implementation_\r\n- [`https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/master/cli/src/cmd/cast/wallet/mod.rs#L77`](https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/master/cli/src/cmd/cast/wallet/mod.rs#L77)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82266083/216162725-dbd7fc12-4835-4f59-8da3-9087075d1ebe.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Running `cargo build `  \r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82266083/216160943-cc88c4ee-cc98-4e08-9ae6-2001f1897b15.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82266083/216163037-8cb08d0f-0552-40d0-8f22-bc7b14003b9c.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n> What other files are involved in the implementation of a new cast command ? I also found a crate [`bip39`](https://crates.io/crates/bip39)  its a bit old, maybe there are some more newer ones which I need to find, and test.",
